id: pm-bnh3
title: Windows background stop progress assertion
description: "Make the background test-run stop regression tolerate platform timing where a linked-test progress heartbeat is recorded after the stop signal, while still asserting the stopped final state."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:ci","area:test-runs",windows
