resolution: Windows stopped background-run progress assertion now tolerates retained linked-test heartbeat fields.
expected_result: Windows regression tests should pass whether the final stopped record sees the test-all end line or a linked-test heartbeat last.
actual_result: "The stopped-run assertion now requires the stable finished/stopped fields and allows retained synthetic linked-test progress values, matching the background-run finalizer behavior across platforms."
